title: Sejuani Mains Club, come join
body:
The club name is "Winter's Waifus" and the tag is " ~SEJ~ ".
Anyone from a full on main to a part time player can join.
All you need to do is just add me "Veldari" on LoL and ask for an invite or join the discord.
https://discord.gg/7ZjNsMD

Get ready to make lots of Sejuani puns otherwise this club will be boaring.
